Class PositionIMPL

java.lang.Object
implementation.PositionIMPL
All Implemented Interfaces:
fr.sorbonne_u.cps.sensor_network.interfaces.PositionI, Serializable
public class PositionIMPL extends Object implements fr.sorbonne_u.cps.sensor_network.interfaces.PositionI

Description

The class PositionIMPL acts as the implementation of the PositionI interface and provides the position of the node in the network.
